Privacy Policy – Captagram
Aureolls is committed to protecting your personal information and ensuring that your privacy is respected. This Privacy Policy applies to the Captagram mobile application (Android App). By using Captagram app, you consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of your personal information as described in this Privacy Policy.
Please note that Captagram is rated for users aged 12 and above. We encourage parents and guardians to monitor their children’s use of the app and to discuss online safety with them.
Information Collection and Use
The App requires your email address and name to create an account. This information is used to identify you as a user of the App and to provide you with access to the App’s features. Your email address may also be used to send you notifications or updates about the App.
We do not share any kind of user data with any third-party. We use the data we collect only for the purposes of providing and improving the App, and for communication with users of the App.
Serving Ads to EEA and UK Users
For users located in the European Economic Area (EEA) and the United Kingdom (UK), the Captagram app includes a Google-certified Consent Management Platform (CMP). As part of our compliance with privacy regulations, we are required to obtain your consent before serving personalized ads or accessing certain types of data.
Consent Requirement
Consent is required to use the app. Upon the first-time launch of the app, you will be presented with a consent form provided by our CMP. This form will explain the purposes for which your data will be used and seek your consent to serve personalized ads.
App Usage Without Consent
Currently, there is no way to use the app without providing ad consent. Once you have given consent or confirmed your choices, you will be able to continue using the app. Please note that the only way to reset your choices or revoke your consent is to uninstall and reinstall the app.
Information Security
We take reasonable steps to protect the personal information we collect from loss, misuse, and unauthorised access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet, or method of electronic storage, is 100% secure. Therefore, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.
Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we make any material changes to this Privacy Policy, we will notify you by means of a notice on the App, or by email to the email address you have provided us.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
aureollabs@gmail.com
Thank you for choosing Captagram.
